metadata.description: Configurable parameters for F.A.R.F.A.N executor methods

D1-Q1.question: Q1
D1-Q1.docstring: Extracts numeric data, reference years, and official sources as baseline.

D1-Q2.question: Q2
D1-Q2.docstring: Quantifies problem magnitude, gaps, and identifies data limitations.

D1-Q3.question: Q3
D1-Q3.docstring: Traces monetary resources assigned to programs in Investment Plan (PPI).

D1-Q4.question: Q4
D1-Q4.docstring: Identifies installed capacity (entities, staff, equipment) and limitations.

D1-Q5.question: Q5
D1-Q5.docstring: Validates scope justification via legal framework and constraint recognition.

D2-Q1.question: Q1
D2-Q1.docstring: Validates structured format of activities (table/matrix with required columns).

D2-Q2.question: Q2
D2-Q2.docstring: Infers intervention logic: instrument (how), target (who), causality (why).

D2-Q3.question: Q3
D2-Q3.docstring: Analyzes linkage between activities and root causes/structural determinants.

D2-Q4.question: Q4
D2-Q4.docstring: Identifies implementation risks and mitigation measures.

D2-Q5.question: Q5
D2-Q5.docstring: Evaluates strategic coherence: complementarity and logical sequence.

D3-Q1.question: Q1
D3-Q1.docstring: Validates indicator quality: baseline, target, source of verification.

D3-Q2.question: Q2
D3-Q2.docstring: DIM03_Q02_PRODUCT_TARGET_PROPORTIONALITY — Analyzes proportionality of targets to the diagnosed universe using canonical D3 notation.

D3-Q3.question: Q3
D3-Q3.docstring: DIM03_Q03_TRACEABILITY_BUDGET_ORG — Validates budgetary and organizational traceability of products under canonical D3 notation.

D3-Q4.question: Q4
D3-Q4.docstring: DIM03_Q04_TECHNICAL_FEASIBILITY — Evaluates activity-product feasibility vs resources/deadlines (canonical D3).

D3-Q5.question: Q5
D3-Q5.docstring: DIM03_Q05_OUTPUT_OUTCOME_LINKAGE — Analyzes mechanisms linking outputs to outcomes with canonical D3 labeling.

D4-Q1.question: Q1
D4-Q1.docstring: DIM04_Q01_OUTCOME_INDICATOR_COMPLETENESS — Validates outcome indicators (baseline, target, horizon) with canonical D4 notation.

D4-Q2.question: Q2
D4-Q2.docstring: Validates explicit causal chain with assumptions and enabling conditions.

D4-Q3.question: Q3
D4-Q3.docstring: Analyzes justification of result ambition based on investment/capacity/benchmarks.

D4-Q4.question: Q4
D4-Q4.docstring: Evaluates whether results address/resolve prioritized problems from diagnosis.

D4-Q5.question: Q5
D4-Q5.docstring: Validates alignment with superior frameworks (PND, SDGs).

D5-Q1.question: Q1
D5-Q1.docstring: Analyzes long-term impacts, transmission routes, and time lags.

D5-Q2.question: Q2
D5-Q2.docstring: DIM05_Q02_COMPOSITE_PROXY_VALIDITY — Validates composite indices/proxies for complex impacts (canonical D5).

D5-Q3.question: Q3
D5-Q3.docstring: Analyzes proxy indicators for intangible impacts with validity documentation.

D5-Q4.question: Q4
D5-Q4.docstring: Evaluates systemic risks that could rupture causal mechanisms.

D5-Q5.question: Q5
D5-Q5.docstring: Analyzes realism of impact ambition and potential unintended effects.

D6-Q1.question: Q1
D6-Q1.docstring: Builds/validates explicit Theory of Change with diagram and assumptions.

D6-Q2.question: Q2
D6-Q2.docstring: Validates logical proportionality: no leaps, intervention matches result scale.

D6-Q3.question: Q3
D6-Q3.docstring: Analyzes validation/testing proposals for weak assumptions before scaling.

D6-Q4.question: Q4
D6-Q4.docstring: Analyzes monitoring system with correction mechanisms and learning processes.

D6-Q5.question: Q5
D6-Q5.docstring: Evaluates contextual adaptation: differential impacts and territorial constraints.
